message.content: {"chain":"mainnet","contract_address":"0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000001","description":"Tracks when new Uniswap V3 pools are created by indexing the PoolCreated event.","event_name":"PoolCreated","event_signature":"PoolCreated(address,address,uint24,int24,address)","indexed_fields":[{"indexed":true,"name":"token0","rust_type":"String","solidity_type":"address"},{"indexed":true,"name":"token1","rust_type":"String","solidity_type":"address"},{"indexed":true,"name":"fee","rust_type":"String","solidity_type":"uint24"},{"indexed":false,"name":"tickSpacing","rust_type":"String","solidity_type":"int24"},{"indexed":false,"name":"pool","rust_type":"String","solidity_type":"address"}],"start_block":0,"table_schema":{"columns":[{"name":"id","type":"BIGSERIAL PRIMARY KEY"},{"name":"block_number","type":"BIGINT NOT NULL"},{"name":"block_timestamp","type":"BIGINT NOT NULL"},{"name":"transaction_hash","type":"VARCHAR(66) NOT NULL"},{"name":"log_index","type":"INTEGER NOT NULL"},{"name":"token0","type":"VARCHAR(42) NOT NULL"},{"name":"token1","type":"VARCHAR(42) NOT NULL"},{"name":"fee","type":"NUMERIC(78, 0) NOT NULL"},{"name":"tick_spacing","type":"NUMERIC(39, 0) NOT NULL"},{"name":"pool","type":"VARCHAR(42) NOT NULL"}],"indexes":["CREATE INDEX idx_block_number ON {table_name}(block_number)","CREATE INDEX idx_timestamp ON {table_name}(block_timestamp)"],"table_name":"uniswap_v3_pool_created"}}
